name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForAIDS
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for AIDS
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to AIDS or CD4 count <200 and is listed as an immunocompromised condition on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes AIDS or CD4 count <200 and AIDS associated disorders (e.g., Aplastic anemia associated with AIDS). It also includes terms related to AIDS complicating pregnancy, childbirth, and the puerperium.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes asymptomatic HIV infection.)
